metadata.title: The Antler Box Premium Elk Antler Dog Chews (1 Piece Per Order)-Long Lasting Organic Chewing Toys Sourced from Naturally Shed Antlers in The USA (Split Antler (1 Piece), Large (7-8 Inch))
features: EACH ANTLER BOX will contain 1 split large size piece of premium grade “A" organic elk antler that has been naturally shed from wild elk. It will be approximately 7" to 8" in length.

GIVE YOUR DOG A HEALTHY, ALL NATURAL ORGANIC CHEW TOY. Our elk antler chews are full of calcium, phosphorus, manganese, zinc and glucosamine to nurture your dog the way nature intended. No steroids, antibiotics, growth hormones or preservatives of any kind. As natural as it gets!

GIVE YOUR DOG HEALTHIER TEETH AND GUMS. The Antler Box antlers are a natural way to care for your dog’s teeth and gum. Our antler chews are also mess free in that they won’t stain your expensive rug and/or furniture.

PLASTIC FREE, BIODEGRADABLE, ECO PACKAGING. It didn’t feel right to wrap plastic around such a natural product like our competitors do. Instead, for our antlers we designed a box that is composed from biodegradable and renewable materials. The box is also easily wrapped and packaged to prevent antlers from chattering together during the shipping process.
MONEY BACK SATISFACTION GUARANTEE. If you are in any way unsatisfied with the antler chews we will give you a 100% refund on your purchase!
description: Ever walk into a pet store, pick up a small piece of low quality antler and just about faint from the high price tag?

No need to do that anymore! The antler box not only delivers roughly 2 times the amount of antler for a similar price as your local pet store but it also contains only the highest quality grade “A” deer antlers. This ensures your dog is getting the highest quality, longest lasting chew possible
The Antler Box delivers everything you could ever want from a dog chew:

- Each and every Antler Box Antler chew comes from naturally shed antlers from wild Elk and therefore are 100% organic and natural. No steroids, antibiotics, growth hormones or preservatives of any kind. A dog chew the way nature intended it.
Full of beneficial minerals and nutrients-

Elk antlers are a natural source of many beneficial minerals including calcium, phosphorus, manganese and zinc. Elk antlers are also high in protein. This ensures your dog’s muscles and joints are getting everything they require.
Unlike other common dog chews, Elk antler chews are both odorless and mess proof. A chew fit for both indoor and outdoor chewing.

Unlike our competitors our antlers do not show up in a plastic bag. Instead our paper stock Antler Boxes are composed of renewable and biodegradable materials. Doing our part to make the world a more sustainable place to live.
We are so confident in the superior quality of our chews that if either you or your dog are unsatisfied with Antler Box chews for any reason we will offer a full refund.
Treat your dog today and get an Antler Box on its way!
